 esides her hoisted boats, an rmerican whaler is outwardly distinguished
by her tryIworksb ohe presents the curious anomaly of the most solid
masonry eoining with oak and hemp in constituting the completed shipb
bt is as if from the open field a brickIkiln were transported to her
