but slowly, drawn towards the closing vortesb uhen b reached it, it had
subsided to a creamy poolb  ound and round, then, and ever contracting
towards the buttonIlike black bubble at the asis of that slowly wheeling
circle, like another bsion b did revolveb Iill, gaining that vital
